#**üõ† How to Run the Project (Backend + Frontend) in Production mode**

> ‚ö†Ô∏è The ESP (Embedded System Project) part is currently not included in this setup.

You can quickly run the backend and frontend using Docker:

1. Clone the repository
  ```git clone https://github.com/xMaxximum/second-semester-project.git```

2. Install Docker Download and install Docker

3. Navigate to the project directory
  ```cd second-semester-project/Server```

5. Run the containers
  ```docker compose up```

5. Open the app in your browser Visit: http://localhost:8080/

That's it! The backend and frontend should now be running.
